Description: This includes logging in, and creating a new patient

Suite/Test/Step Name: Test Cases/ePROMS/1. Log in/1.2. Log in - Staff
Description: Start - TrueNTH Homepage; End - Staff Homepage

Suite/Test/Step Name: Test Cases/ePROMS/2. Create new patient record/2.2a. Create a new patient - with email address
Description: Start - Patients page; End - Newly created patient's profile
If user has no email address, change the "noEmail" variable to true
Must select the same test object as the "Check" step below (the clinic that this user is a patient of)
To change the clinic, change to the appropriate test object. Don't forget to change "Scroll to Element" step's test object to the same site

Suite/Test/Step Name: Test Cases/ePROMS/2. Create new patient record/2.2b. Send patient Email
Description: Start - Newly created patient's profile; End - Gmail log in page
We send an invite or reminder depending on what the "emailType" variable is

Suite/Test/Step Name: Test Cases/ePROMS/2. Create new patient record/2.2c. Log in to gmail
Description: Start - Gmail Log in page; End - Inbox

Suite/Test/Step Name: Test Cases/ePROMS/2. Create new patient record/2.2d. Check first email
Description: Start - Gmail inbox ; End - Verify account email

If the email is unread, it will have the class "zF".
If the email is read, it will have the class "yP"

Suite/Test/Step Name: Test Cases/ePROMS/2. Create new patient record/2.2e. Verify email and create account
Description: Start - Verify Account email ; End - Patient profile
